description:
In this Everything Iconic POP Dive, Danny welcomes the wonderful Hannah Brown (host of the Brown-Eyed Jewnicorn podcast) to talk about the 1998 Halloween classic Practical Magic. They discuss favorite moments, Queen Sandra and Queen Nicole, USA's Suits, and SO much more.


*To support this podcast & for bonus episodes, visit www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
